OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782751678
OL,3,CFamily's tribute to 'lovely, cheeky'
OL,4,Cboy, 13, who died in lake
OL,6,FThe family of a 13-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fdied after entering a lake in
OL,8,FLeicestershire during the recent
OL,9,Fheatwave have paid tribute to him.
OL,11,FHayden Jones-Powell has been
OL,12,Fremembered by his family as a cheeky,
OL,13,Fgorgeous boy who loved animals and had
OL,14,Feverything going for him.
OL,16,FHayden, a keen West Bromwich Albion
OL,17,Fsupporter with a wide circle of
OL,18,Ffriends, had gone to cool off in the
OL,19,Fwater with friends after school when
OL,20,Fhe got into difficulty.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
