OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782751678
OL,3,CFamily's tribute to 'lovely, cheeky'
OL,4,Cboy, 13, who died in lake
OL,6,FHis Aunt Charlotte Powell said, "He
OL,7,Fwas just a really lovely little cheeky
OL,8,Fboy," she said, adding that he had
OL,9,Flots of friends and "did really,
OL,10,Freally well at school."
OL,12,FPolice were called just after 1.30 pm,
OL,13,Fwith Leicestershire Fire and Rescue
OL,14,FService and East Midlands Ambulance
OL,15,FService also attending. Specialist
OL,16,Fdive teams launched a search of the
OL,17,Flake, where they found Hayden.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
