OL,3,CFamily's tribute to 'lovely, cheeky'
OL,4,Cboy, 13, who died in lake
OL,6,FOfficers said there is no suggestion
OL,7,Fof any suspicious circumstances, and
OL,8,Fthat a file will be prepared for the
OL,9,Fcoroner.
OL,11,FA fundraiser has been set up to help
OL,12,Fthe family give Hayden "a beautiful
OL,13,Fsend-off"; it's raised almost #15,000
OL,14,Fso far.
